{"tid":2016304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又現浮屍 本周第5具民眾毛骨悚然","createTime":"2020-05-14T09:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T10:40:45.000Z","uid":229185,"like":39,"dislike":232,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"4650710f76dfa85d6644a0bcb34e9a55e88ac6b0","tid":2016304,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:47:13.000Z","msg":"基隆河6號水門又現浮屍 本周第5具民眾毛骨悚然<br />\n<br />\n台北市基隆河面又出現浮屍，已經是本周以來第五具，連警消都感覺不可思議而毛骨悚然。上午8點多有民眾前往民權橋大佳河濱公園運動，6號水門附近河邊時，見到一具屍體在水面上漂動，警消利用出動橡皮艇將浮屍打撈上岸後，發現拉回岸邊，由於屍體已腫脹無法辨識，初步檢視無外傷，警方已採集指紋比對釐清身分。<br />\n<br />\n台北市在本月8、9兩日，在南港、北投、士林、大直等地接連發現4起浮屍，令人毛骨悚然，警方初步調查，研判4名死者應該都是輕生，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無他殺嫌疑</span></span>，詳細發生原因正由檢警調查中。<br />\n<br />\n台灣版： 無可疑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚嬲"},{"pid":"845b66aaf4db6016c872af6c786de2391b371a52","tid":2016304,"uid":41873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://legcopetition.wixsite.com/form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegcopetition.wixsite.com%2Fform&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7pugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=18d43160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legcopetition.wixsite.com/form</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立法會三不投聯署</span></span></strong> 就黎deadline啦<br />\n大家簽完記得share埋俾你地身邊既同路人呀"},{"pid":"97cf39440b72854536920d4ca76fb01aee0d13e6","tid":2016304,"uid":192409,"like":21,"dislike":82,"score":-61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45de0e722cf72eb0e76da286fb0c95af50a58073","tid":2016304,"uid":229185,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"cite